// Regression test for P-1 (audit 2026-05-06): translator must memoise
// shared SAWCore subterms or the emitted .lean grows as 2^N for an
// N-deep doubling chain. See DagSharing.cry for the full story.
//
// The .lean.good file pins a SMALL emission. If the let-sharing pass
// regresses, this driver's emitted .lean diverges sharply (size
// blows up exponentially in N) and the test fails the diff long
// before it OOMs in CI.

write_lean_cryptol_module "DagSharing.cry" "test_cryptol_module_dag_sharing.module.lean" [] [];
